<!-- wp:paragraph {"style":{"typography":{"lineHeight":"var:custom|line-height|body"}},"fontSize":"200"} -->
<p class="has-200-font-size" style="line-height:var(--wp--custom--line-height--body)"><?php esc_html_e( 'The House of Fire celebrates the creation of brandy. Brandy in South Africa is produced in two ways — a potstill or a blended brandy. A potstill brandy is double distilled in a potstill and, by SA legislation, matured for at least 3 years in oak; our exquisite KWV 10, 12, 15 and 20 year, Nexus and Centenary brandies are potstill brandies. A blended brandy must contain at least 30% potstill brandy matured for at least 3 years in oak, with the rest a column-distilled wine spirit; our customer favourite KWV 3 year and 5 year brandies are blended brandies. We invite you on a journey that will ignite the senses.', 'kwv' ); ?></p>
